<library name="con-headers">
<description>&lt;h2&gt;Pin and Socket Headers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;author&gt;bbarnt@gmail.com&lt;/author&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Parts are organized 
by &lt;b&gt;MA&lt;/b&gt;le or &lt;b&gt;FE&lt;/b&gt;male, then the number of positions, and the width.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are (3) versions 
of each, so that there are different 3D models attached to each:&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;-DNP for bare pads, no 3D model&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;no suffix for standard lead parts&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;-L for Long Tail (i.e. PC/104, etc)&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
