<sheet>
<description>LCC &amp; RS-485 Communications</description>
<plain>
<text x="215.9" y="10.16" size="4.445" layer="97" align="center">COMMUNICATIONS</text>
<text x="261.62" y="10.16" size="3.81" layer="97" align="center">AR2</text>
<text x="147.32" y="198.12" size="3.81" layer="97" align="top-left">Calculations for CAN Current:
</text>
<text x="152.4" y="193.04" size="2.54" layer="97" align="top-left">Desired Range: 0-500 mA
INA180A1 Gain: 20 V/V
Rsense &lt; PDmax/ Imax * Imax
Rsense &lt; 1 w/ 0.5 * 0.5 » &lt; 2 Ω
Vsp = Vs - 0.03 V » 3.27
Vsn = Vgnd + 0.005 » 0.005
Vsp &gt; Imax * Rsense * Gain
Vsp &gt; 0.5 * 0.3 * 20 » 3 [OK]
Vsn &lt;  Imin * Rsense * Gain
Vsn &lt; 0 * 0.3 * 20 » 0 [OK]
A8 (max) = Imax * Rsense * Gain
A8 (max) = 0.5 * 0.3 * 20 » 3 V = 500 mA
A8 resolution = A8 (max) / 4096 = 0.5 / 4096 = 
0.12 mA per count
</text>
<text x="175.26" y="104.14" size="2.54" layer="97" align="top-left">RS-485 TERMINATION: JUMPER JP6 INSTALLED
RS-485 BIASING: INSTALL JP5 &amp; JP7

CAN TERMINATION: EXTERNAL</text>
<text x="264.16" y="40.64" size="1.778" layer="97" align="bottom-right">*FILTER CAPACITORS FOR: U1, U2, IC4</text>
</plain>
